install qt4 libraries from sources or from your distribution

Note on ubuntu : installing qt4 from package don't replace the symlink of moc. Use qmake-qt4 instead of qmake (or recreate the symlink) and replace the symlink of moc : rm /etc/alternatives/moc ; ln -s /usr/bin/moc-qt4 /etc/alternatives/moc

You need to install boost development package to get libtorrent working :
 - Boost::DateTime
 - Boost::Filesystem
 - Boost::Thread
 - Boost::Serialization

You need to install libgpgme to get GPG signing working 